---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Gaudette AI builds the Brain Network — AI knowledge infrastructure that compounds over time.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 text-center">
      <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-amber-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">About</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-warm-900 leading-tight mb-6">
        Built by practitioners,<br/>for practitioners
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-warm-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We built the Brain Network to solve our own problem: AI that forgets everything.
        Now it powers how we run our entire company.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin Story -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-8">
        <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mb-5"></div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-4">The origin</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          In early 2026, Frederic Gaudette was running consulting projects across
          multiple clients, each with their own context, decisions, and history. AI tools
          were powerful but amnesic &mdash; every conversation started from scratch.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The solution wasn't better prompts. It was better architecture. What if AI could
          maintain persistent memory across sessions? What if multiple specialized agents
          could share context intelligently? What if knowledge compounded instead of vanishing?
        </p>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-700 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          That insight became the Brain Network &mdash; and the Knowledge That Compounds
          methodology behind it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
            Make AI knowledge persistent and cumulative. Every person and team should have
            AI that gets smarter over time, not AI that starts from zero every session.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-3">Philosophy</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
            AI should assist, not replace. Human judgment stays in the loop. Every decision
            point is auditable. You own your data. Knowledge compounds because you
            chose to invest in it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Facts -->
  <section class="pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900">Company</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-5 text-center">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-1">2026</p>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-warm-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Founded</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-5 text-center">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-1">QC</p>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-warm-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Sherbrooke</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-5 text-center">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-1">BYOK</p>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-warm-500 uppercase tracking-wider">AI model</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-5 text-center">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-warm-900 mb-1">100%</p>
          <p class="text-[12px] text-warm-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Browser-based</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Use -->
  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-4">We eat our own cooking</h2>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Gaudette AI runs entirely on the Brain Network. Our OPS Brain coordinates
          sprints. Our COD Brain builds the product. Our Marketing Brain writes content.
          Every decision, every document, every piece of context lives in our own system.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
          When we say knowledge compounds, we mean it. We've been accumulating institutional
          knowledge in our Brain Network since day one, and it gets more valuable every week.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- KTC Methodology Link -->
  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/methodology" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7 hover:border-warm-900 transition-colors group">
          <p class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-amber-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Methodology</p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">Knowledge That Compounds</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
            The five principles behind everything we build. Read the methodology &rarr;
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/faq" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-warm-300 p-7 hover:border-warm-900 transition-colors group">
          <p class="text-[12px] font-semibold text-amber-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Questions?</p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-warm-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors">Frequently asked questions</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
            Everything you need to know about the Brain Network &rarr;
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="bg-warm-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-warm-50 mb-3">Start building your AI knowledge</h2>
        <p class="text-[15px] text-warm-400 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          14-day free trial. No credit card required. Your OPS Brain sets everything up.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
          <a href="https://app.gaudetteai.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-warm-50 text-warm-900 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-[15px] hover:bg-white transition-colors">
            Start Free Trial
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:contact@gaudetteai.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-warm-400 border border-warm-700 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-[15px] hover:text-warm-50 hover:border-warm-400 transition-colors">
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
